'Yan majalisa na Wales sun nuna damuwarsu cewa za a ɗauke su a matsayin 'yan tsana.
Wasu mambobin majalisar sun nuna rashin jin daɗinsu bayan sun ji shawarar canza sunan matsayinsu a matsayin MWP (Mambobin Majalisar Dokokin Wales).
Wannan ra'ayin ya samo asali ne bayan an samar da tsare-tsaren canza sunan majalisa na majalisa na Wales.
Mambobin majalisar siyasa na tsoron cewa wannan shiri zai zama abin dariya a gare su.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Labour a majalisar ya ce a cikin harshen Turanci, "Twp" da kuma "Pwp" suna yin karin magana da sunan.
Idan ka fito daga wajen Wales: a cikin harshen Welsh, twp na nufin inozo kuma pwp na nufin shit.
A nata bangaren, wani dan majalisa na Scotland ya ce duk kungiyar ba ta da farin ciki sosai kuma ta ba da shawarar neman wasu sunaye.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Conservative Party of Wales ya ce yana da sha'awar sake canza sunan, amma kuma ya nuna damuwarsa game da abin da zai iya haifar da canjin MWP.
Don fahimtar wannan rikici, ya kamata a lura cewa haruffan W na Wales da u na Turanci na Yorkshire suna da irin wannan furci.
A gefe guda, kwamitin taron, wanda ke samar da tsarin doka don sauya sunaye, ya ce: Dangane da membobin taron, za su kasance da alhakin zaɓar masu bayyanawa da suke so su yi amfani da su.
A karkashin Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017, Majalisar Wales tana da ikon canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta buga sakamakon binciken jama'a don zaɓar shawarwarin da aka ba da shawara kuma, gabaɗaya, sunan Majalisar Dokokin Wales ya sami jimlar jimlar goyon baya.
Dangane da sunayen membobin majalisar, Hukumar ta zaɓi sunan Memba na Majalisar Dokoki na Wales ko WMP (a cikin siginan Turanci), amma an yanke shawarar sunan MWP da aka zaɓa a cikin tuntuɓar jama'a.
Mambobin majalisar, a gefe guda, suna ba da shawarar madadin, amma yana iya zama da wuya sosai a zabi wani zaɓi tare da baki ɗaya; musamman ga shugaban majalisar, Elin Jones, wanda dole ne ya aika da zane-zane tare da canje-canje a cikin 'yan makonni.
Koyaya, dokokin da za a yi canje-canje za su shafi aikin taron; a tsakanin sauran abubuwa, za a ƙirƙiri ƙa'idodi don hana ayyukan da za su iya kawo rashin mutunci ga membobin taron kuma za a gudanar da tsarin tsarin taron tare da taimakon wannan doka.
A lokacin da ake tattauna batun sauya dokokin, 'yan majalisa za su sami damar yanke shawara a kan sunayensu.
