Peter Jones ya yi fushi bayan Holly Willoughby ta janye tayin fam miliyan 11
Tauraron shirin Dragons Den Peter Jones ya tafi cikin fushi bayan mai gabatar da gidan talabijin Holly Willoughby ya soke tayin fam miliyan 11 da ya shafi kasuwancin alamar dindindin saboda yana son mai da hankali kan sabbin kwangilarsa tare da Marks da Spencer da ITV.
Willoughby ba shi da lokaci don Truly, wanda ke sayar da kayan gida da kayan abinci.
An kwatanta kasuwancin su da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop.
Mai gabatar da shirin This Morning, mai shekara 37, ya yi amfani da Instagram don sanar da murabus.
Bayan da Holly Willoughby ya yi murabus don karɓar kwangila da aka ba ta daga Marks & Spencer da ITV, tauraron wasan kwaikwayon "Dragons" Den Peter Jones ya yi fushi sosai saboda barin kasuwancin da ya haifar da su a minti na karshe.
Majiyoyinmu sun ce, a ranar Talata an yi wani taro mai cike da tashin hankali a hedkwatar Marlow, kuma sakamakon haka, Jones ya yi fushi sosai lokacin da ya ji bayanin daga shahararren jaridarmu ta TV cewa za ta amince da sabon kwangilar fam miliyan 1.5 kuma saboda haka ba za ta iya ba da lokaci ga kayayyakin gida na Truly ba.
An kwatanta kasuwancin da Gwyneth Paltrow ta Goop kuma ya ninka dukiyar Willoughby na fam miliyan 11.
Willoughby, mai shekaru 37, ya bar kasuwancin Truly a Instagram bayan ya bayyana cewa Jones ya bar Birtaniya don zuwa gidan hutu.
Wata majiya ta ce, wannan abu ne da ya fi muhimmanci ga Holly.
Wannan shawarar za ta tabbatar da rayuwarsa na shekaru ashirin masu zuwa.
Duk da haka, shawarar da ya yanke na barin alamar ta sa mu mamaki.
Babu wanda zai iya gaskata abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, lokacin da aka rufe sayar da alamar.
A gaskiya ma, ajiyar kayayyaki a Marlow tana cike da kayayyakin da ake sayarwa.
A cewar masana, kamfanin yana gab da rasa miliyoyin fam saboda barin mai gabatar da shirin This Morning (wanda shine mai gabatar da mafi riba a Burtaniya); kamfanin ya saka hannun jari mai yawa a cikin samfuran daban-daban (ciki har da matashin kai, kyandir, tufafi da kayayyakin gida) kuma yanzu dole ne ya fuskanci jinkiri da zai iya haifar da shi.
Kuma wannan rikici zai iya kawo ƙarshen abokantaka.
Willoughby da mijinta Dan Baldwin suna da 'ya'ya uku kuma Jones da matarsa, Tara Capp, sun kasance abokai na shekaru goma.
Willoughby da Capp sun kafa Truly a cikin 2016 kuma Jones, 52, ya shiga matsayin darektan a watan Maris.
Dukansu ma'aurata suna shirya hutu tare, kuma Jones yana da kashi 40 cikin 100 na kamfanin samar da talabijin na Baldwin.
Willoughby zai zama jakadan M&S kuma zai maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin I'm A Celebrity na tashar ITV.
Wata majiya a cikin kungiyar Jones ta bayyana jiya da dare cewa ba zai bayyana komai ba game da ayyukan kasuwancinsa.
Mun yi taɗi mai wuya, amma sai muka ƙaunaci juna.
