Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli labaran Talata a tashar Channel Six, da suka nuna cewa 'yan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da Christine Blasey Ford sun zargi Kavanaugh da cin zarafin da ya sha a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, rikici na siyasa ya ci gaba, kuma masu gabatar da shirye-shiryen sun dakatar da shirye-shiryen ranar Juma'a don gabatar da labarai na minti na karshe yayin da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi yarjejeniya da FBI don gudanar da bincike na mako guda.
A cewar abin da Ford ya fada wa majalisar dattawa, ya tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya taba shi sau da yawa yayin da yake cikin maye kuma ya yi kokarin cire tufafinsa a wani biki na makarantar sakandare.
A cikin wata sanarwa mai cike da sha'awa da Kavanaugh ya bayar, ya ce ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
A cewar Nielsen, kimanin mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli sanarwar ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya ƙididdige matsakaicin masu kallo na tashoshin CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Koyaya, wannan lambar ba ta da amfani nan da nan ga sauran tashoshin da suka ba da sanarwar; ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Bugu da ƙari, Nielsen yawanci yana da matsala wajen ƙidaya mutanen da suke kallon talabijin a ofis.
Misali, za mu iya kwatanta yawan masu kallo da wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko lambar yabo ta Academy.
A Fox News Channel, kalaman Kavanaugh sun kasance cikakke ga masu gabatar da shirin kuma sun kai kimanin mutane miliyan 5.69 yayin da yake gabatar da jawabin, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ta kasance ta biyu tare da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta samu miliyan 3,1, NBC ta samu miliyan 2,94, MSNBC ta samu miliyan 2,89 kuma CNN ta samu miliyan 2,52, a cewar Nielsen.
