Bayan sanarwar da jam'iyyar Republican ta yi cewa za ta kada kuri'a a kan Kavanaugh, kyamarorin CNN da CBS sun kama Kavanaugh a ranar Juma'a a cikin masu zanga-zanga yayin da yake kokarin hawa lif don yin jawabi a taron majalisa.
