Yana da wasu jarumai.
Kyaftin Halkett ya yi aiki mai ban mamaki wajen tsara da kuma sarrafa kariya mai ban mamaki, wanda ya sa Menga ya sa Connor Goldson da Joe Worrall su kasance cikin damuwa a duk wasan.
Amma Rangers ba su da abin da za su yi.
Suna aiki sosai a lokacin da suke ƙarƙashin jagorancin Gerrard, amma sun manta da mizanin da kocin ya kafa.
Wasan karshe ya kasance mai rauni kuma sun doke kare gida sau daya kawai, kuma dole ne Rangers suyi sauri idan suna son su fita daga tsakiyar allon.
An yi wa Erdogan maraba a birnin Köln
Murmushi da shuɗi sun yi yawa a ranar Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, lokacin da shugabannin Turkiya da Jamus suka taru don cin abincin safe a Berlin.
Ranar karshe ce ta ziyarar da shugaba Erdogan ya kai Jamus, wadda aka shirya don daidaita dangantakar da ke tsakanin 'yan kawancen NATO.
Sun tattauna batutuwa da dama, ciki har da rashin 'yancin dan adam da' yancin 'yan jarida da kuma shiga Turkiyya a Tarayyar Turai.
Bayan haka, Erdogan ya tafi Cologne don bude wani babban masallaci.
Birnin yana da mafi yawan yawan jama'ar Turkiyya a waje da Turkiyya.
Saboda matakan tsaro da 'yan sanda suka kafa, an hana mutane 25,000 da ke son yin taro a gaban masallacin, amma wasu magoya bayansu sun taru don ganin shugaban.
Daruruwan masu zanga-zangar adawa da Erdogan (mafi yawansu Kurdawa) sun hada muryoyinsu don nuna adawa da manufofin Erdogan da kuma shawarar da gwamnatin Jamus ta yanke na maraba da shugaban.
Rashin amincewa da shugaban ya nuna a bangarorin biyu na zanga-zangar, wasu Turkawa a Jamus suna kiransa gwarzo wasu kuma suna cewa shi kawai mai mulkin kai ne.
