Mista Gendon ya bayyana cewa a cikin al'ummar parapentists, sa'o'i bayan da aka sanar da cewa an rushe Roa Roa Hotel, ya ci gaba da aika saƙonnin WhatsApp ga masu fafatawa, waɗanda ke cikin bikin rairayin bakin teku.
