Kanye West: ya canza sunansa zuwa Ye
Kanye West ya canza sunansa zuwa Ye.
A ranar Asabar ya sanar da canjin a shafinsa na Twitter, yana cewa "wani abu da aka sani da Kanye West".
West, mai shekaru 41, ya yi amfani da cutar ta Ye na wani lokaci, kuma ya yi amfani da wannan cutar a matsayin taken littafinsa na takwas wanda ya fitar a watan Yuni.
Ya yi canjin ne kafin ya fito a shirin "Saturday Night Live" inda ake sa ran Yandi zai gabatar da sabon album dinsa.
Ta shiga wasan kwaikwayon a madadin Ariana Grande, a cewar mahaliccin wasan kwaikwayon, wanda ba zai iya shiga ba saboda dalilai na motsin rai.
Baya ga kasancewa gajartaccen sunan sana'arsa na yanzu, West ya nuna cewa kalmar tana da ma'anar addini a gare shi.
"Ina ganin 'ye' ita ce kalma da aka fi amfani da ita a cikin Littafi Mai-Tsarki kuma tana nufin zu a cikin Littafi Mai-Tsarki", West ya bayyana kwanan nan, yana magana game da kundi tare da mai gabatar da rediyo Big Boy.
"Don haka ni ne kai, ni ne mu, mu ne.
Ya fito ne daga Kanye, wanda yake nufin "ka zama Ye" - mai nuna mana nagarta da mugunta da rikice-rikice da komai.
Wannan aikin ya fi nuna ko wane ne mu".
Yana ɗaya daga cikin shahararrun masu rap da suka canja sunansu.
Sean Combs an san shi da suna Puff Daddy, P. Diddy ko Diddy, amma a wannan shekara ya nuna cewa ya fi son sunayen ƙauna da Brother Love.
Jay-Z, wanda ya yi aiki tare da West, ya canza ƙananan haruffa da manyan haruffa.
