Taron Trump a Yammacin Virginia, Tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai kaddamar da gangamin yakin neman zabe a wannan daren a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan Trump biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, kuma zai ziyarci wurare da dama da abokansa suka yi, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da yake jiran kuri'ar da za ta tabbatar da shi a matsayin babban lauya, Trump yana neman goyon baya ko kuma samun goyon baya a zaben tsakiyar lokaci, inda 'yan Republican ke fuskantar asarar iko a majalisa a zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump na yau a West Virginia kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon shi a Intanet?
Za a fara ziyarar Trump a West Virginia da karfe 7 na yamma a yau Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Kamar dai Trump zai gudanar da sauraron sauraron da aka yi a wannan makon kan wanda aka nada a matsayin babban lauya na kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, har sai majalisar dattijai ta tabbatar da shi, wanda ya yi zabe a kan rashin amincewa da shi, a yayin da ake ci gaba da binciken FBI kan halin da bai dace ba.
Amma babban manufar wannan rangadin na tarurruka shi ne don taimakawa 'yan Republican su sami wasu kuri'u a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
"Kampen shugaban kasa Trump ya ce manufar tarurruka biyar na mako mai zuwa shine a sake farfado da masu sa kai da kuma taimakawa wajen rike rinjayen 'yan Republican a majalisar dattijai da kuma majalisar wakilai".
"Taron na da matukar muhimmanci kuma shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama a yayin zaman yakin neman zabensa", in ji mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda bai yarda ya bayyana sunansa ba.
Taron da aka shirya a filin wasa na Wesbanco a Wheeling, zai baiwa magoya bayan kungiyar a Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma kafofin yada labarai na Pittsburgh damar samun labarin, kamar yadda West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai kai ziyara karo na biyu a watan jiya a jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe zaben 2016 da kashi 40 cikin dari.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa Sanata Patrick Morrisey na Jam'iyyar Republican daga Virginia, wanda yake binsa.
Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa zai je can don taimakawa wajen gudanar da zabensa ba, in ji Simon Header, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Amurka za ta yi kokarin ci gaba da zama a gasar Ryder Cup na ranar Lahadi
Bayan wasanni uku na wasa guda, an ga cewa wasan hudu na ranar Asabar ya samu abin da gasar Ryder Cup take bukata.
A yanzu, batun shi ne, ra'ayin da 'yan wasa suka yi imani da shi, amma ba a yi amfani da shi ba a sauran wasanni.
To, a ina za ka ce lokaci ne yanzu?
"Suna da maki shida a gaba kuma yanzu suna da maki hudu, don haka ina ganin yanzu ne lokaci, a wata hanya", in ji Jordan Spieth, a lokacin da yake yin rana daya.
A bayyane yake, Turai tana da maki hudu a kan 12 da ke cikin wasa.
Kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, Amurkawa suna jin cewa iska ba ta son su, kuma suna bukatar taimako, musamman daga Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka yi wasa tare kuma suka sami maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Spieth ya kasance mai mahimmanci daga daidaita zuwa kore, kuma yana yin misali.
Wannan muryar murna ta kara kara kara kara yayin da zagaye ke ci gaba, kuma ya kammala wani muhimmin bugun jini, ya lashe hudu na dukkan-square, bayan da Thomas ya rasa biyu bayan biyu.
Ya yi bikin tare da wani ihu mai kama da nasara a wasan 15, yana nuna cewa tawagar Amurka ba ta fita daga gasar ba.
"Ka yi ƙoƙari ka sami ƙarfinka kuma ka mai da hankali ga wasanka", in ji Spieth.
Abin da ya rage wa 'yan wasan.
Za mu yi rami 18.
'Yan wasa guda daya da suka ci Spieth da Thomas a kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, 'yan wasan tarihi na gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Ma'aurata hudu daga cikin hudu na Turai masu ban mamaki amma masu ban sha'awa sun yi alkawarin rashin nasara.
"Moliwood" ne kawai ma'aurata da ba su yi wasa da kullun ranar Asabar ba, amma a ranar Asabar da safe, da kuma ranar Jumma'a da yamma, sun guje wa kullun, kuma a ranar Jumma'a sun kasance a cikin tara.
Wannan juyi da taron jama'a da makamashi da ke zuwa daga gare su sun sanya su zama ma'aurata da za a shawo kansu a ranar Lahadi kuma babu wani ɗan wasan Turai da ya fi Fleetwood da Molina da ya rufe nasarar Turai lokacin da rana ta fito a Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau su shiga rami daban-daban tare.
Amma, da wuri ne a yi magana game da manyan Turawa.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun hanzarta aikin Sergio Garcia, wanda ya kasance a cikin kwata-kwata, wanda ya daidaita da Alex Noren.
Sun sanya bogey da biyu a gaba a kan rami wanda ba a taɓa samun kusa da shi ba don cin nasarar Spaniard da Swede.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai taimake ka ka fitar da kanka daga cikin ramin.
Hudu ɗin sun yi sha'awar ganin yadda ma'aurata suke hulɗa da juna, da irin shawarwarin da suke bayarwa da waɗanda ba sa bayarwa, da kuma yadda za a iya canja dabarun a lokaci guda.
Turai ta yi kyau a matsayin tawagar, kuma tana da babban matsayi a wasan karshe, amma wasan hudu ya nuna cewa tawagar Amurka tana da ƙarfin gwiwa don yin gwagwarmaya, duk da cewa wasu, musamman Stateside, sun yi shakku.
Turai ta yi nasara da maki 10-6 a wasan karshe na gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Turai ta yi nasara a wasan karshe na gasar cin kofin Ryder bayan da 'yan wasan hudu suka ci 10-6 a ranar Asabar a kan Amurka.
Ma'aurata masu wahayi zuwa ga Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molina sun sami nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods mai ƙoƙari, kuma sun sami maki huɗu masu daraja a Le Golf Nationale.
Thomas Bjorn na Turai, yana kokarin dawo da kyautar da Hazelin ya rasa shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ya yi nasara da safe, kuma ya lashe gasar 3-1.
