Jim Fury ya bukaci maki takwas a wasanni 12 da suka buga a ranar Lahadi don ya ci nasara.
Fleetwood shine kawai dan wasan Turai wanda ya ci maki hudu a jere kuma tare da Molinari, wanda bayan babban karshen mako da ake kira "Molliwood", sun kasance na biyu a tarihin gasar cin kofin Ryder ta lashe maki hudu a wasanni hudu.
