Yanzu kuma shafi na mu na "Sunday Morning" ranar 30 ga watan Satumba, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka wuce, a ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
