Sabon maganin rigakafin cutar kansa zai iya koyar da garkuwar jikinka ta gano kuma ta kashe kwayoyin cutar.
Rigakafin yana koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki gane kwayoyin cutar a matsayin wani ɓangare na magani.
Duk abin da suke yi shi ne, su kwashe kwayoyin garkuwar jiki daga cikin marasa lafiya, sannan su canza su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Sai su duba wannan furotin da ya zama ruwan dare ga yawancin cututtukan daji, sannan su sake yin allurar.
Wannan allurar rigakafin da muke gwaji da ita tana da sakamako mai kyau a kan marasa lafiya da nau'ikan ciwon daji daban-daban.
A gaskiya, wata mace da aka yi mata maganin rigakafi wanda yake koyar da tsarin garkuwarta yadda zai gane kwayoyin cutar, ta samu damar kawar da cutar kansa ta ovarian fiye da watanni 18.
Hanyarmu ita ce, mu cire dukkan kwayoyin garkuwar jikin mutum daga cikin marasa lafiya, mu canza su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje domin su iya ganin wani furotin da ake kira HER2, wanda ya zama ruwan dare ga yawancin masu ciwon daji, sannan mu sake saka su cikin kwayar.
Jay Berzofsky a Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon daji ta kasa a Bethesda, Maryland, ta ce, "Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa muna da maganin rigakafi mai matukar kyau".
