An samu sama da sabbin mutane 40,000 da suka kamu da cutar a cikin kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin shari'o'in cutar sun shafi cutar da ake yadawa ta hanyar jima'i, kuma wannan canji ne daga abin da ya gabata.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri ta hanyar jinin da aka shayar da shi a wasu yankuna na kasar Sin.
Amma a wannan hanyar, adadin masu kamuwa da cutar HIV ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili, kamar yadda jami'an lafiya na kasar Sin suka ce a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya karu da mutum 100,000 a kowace shekara.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a tsakanin al'ummar LGBT a China.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT ya zama ruwan dare.
Saboda dabi'u masu ra'ayin mazan jiya na kasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70-90 na mazajen da suke yin jima'i da mazaje suna yin aure da mace.
Yawancin cututtuka da ke faruwa a cikin jima'i suna faruwa ne ta hanyar yin amfani da kariya ta jima'i.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta bada umarnin samun magani na cutar HIV a ko'ina a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
