Menene bikin dan kasa da kasa kuma shin ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar za a yi bikin Global Citizen a birnin New York, wani biki na shekara-shekara na kiɗa da ke kawo manyan masu fasaha tare da manufa mai muhimmanci: kawar da talauci a duniya.
A karo na 17 a wannan karon, bikin na Global Citizen zai kawo dubban mutane zuwa Grand Square na Central Park, ba wai kawai don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don haɓaka wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron, wanda shine kawar da matsanancin talauci kafin shekarar 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda aka kafa a shekarar 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wani kungiya ne na kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Don karɓar tikiti kyauta don taron (idan ba ku da niyyar biyan tikitin VIP), waɗanda suke son halartar wasan kwaikwayon dole ne su yi ayyuka ko "ayyuka" kamar aika saƙon imel ga shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya ko kuma wata hanyar da ta dace don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da manufar kawar da talauci.
Amma wane irin nasara ne Global Citizen ta samu a cikin shekaru 12 da suka rage?
Shin ra'ayin karfafa mutane su dauki mataki ne ta hanyar yin wasan kwaikwayo kyauta, ko kuwa wani misali ne na abin da ake kira clicktivism, wanda yake sa mutane su ji cewa suna kawo canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda ko aika tweet?
Tun daga shekarar 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta samu fiye da "ayyuka" miliyan 19 daga mabiyanta, suna matsawa don cimma manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce, wadannan ayyuka sun sa shugabannin duniya su sanar da manufofi da alkawura masu darajar sama da dala biliyan 37, manufofi da alkawuran da za su shafi rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 kafin shekarar 2030.
A farkon shekarar 2018, kungiyar ta ambaci alkawura da alkawura 390 da suka samo asali daga ayyukan, wanda akalla dala biliyan 10 aka biya ko aka karba.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka tabbatar sun yi tasiri kai tsaye a kan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, "taron masu zuba jari da masu aiwatar da ayyuka da ke da alhakin taimakawa yara wajen bunkasa cikakkiyar damar su, wanda ke da hedikwata a Burtaniya". Ya yi alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda don kawar da rashin abinci a kasar, bayan karbar tweets sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
"Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da agaji, gwamnatocin kasa da kuma 'yan kungiyar Global Citizen kamar ku, za mu mayar da rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki tarihi", in ji jakadan The Power of Nutrition Tracey Ullman a wani jawabi a wani taron kai tsaye a London a watan Afrilu na shekarar 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan ta yi ayyuka sama da 5,000 a Birtaniya don inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa za ta ba da kuɗin aikin Power of Nutrition, wanda zai taimaka wa mata da yara miliyan biyar ta hanyar ayyukan da suka shafi abinci mai gina jiki.
Don amsar wannan tambayar da ake yawan yi a shafin, me ya sa kuke tunanin za mu iya kawar da matsanancin talauci?"
Global Citizen ta amsa, "Za a yi doguwar hanya mai wuya, kuma za mu yi kasala a wasu lokatai.
Amma kamar manyan ƙungiyoyin kare hakkin bil'adama da na nuna wariyar launin fata da suka riga suka zo, za mu yi nasara, tare da ƙarfi.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B da Janelle Monae za su kasance a cikin wasan kwaikwayon a wannan shekara a New York. Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su gabatar da wasan kwaikwayon.
