Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da kai hari da tallan farfaganda
Bayan wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani talla mai shafuka hudu da ke tallata amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China a wata jaridar kungiyar tarayyar kasashen Turai, jakadan Amurka ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfagandar sa.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi tsokaci a ranar Laraba a kan karin kudin da aka biya a jaridar Des Moines Register na kasar Sin, jaridar da ta fi sayar da littattafai a jihar Iowa, bayan da ya zargi kasar Sin da yin kutse a zaben da aka yi ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
Zargin da aka yi wa Beijing na shiga cikin zaben Amurka ya nuna cewa Trump ya sake nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka fada wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters, a wani sabon mataki na Washington na matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
Duk da cewa al'ada ce gwamnatoci na kasashen waje su sanya tallace-tallace domin su inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin yakin kasuwanci mai tasowa wanda kowace kasa ke sanya takunkumi kan kayan da sauran ke shigowa da su.
Tashin hankalin da China ta yi na daukar fansa a farkon yakin cinikayya, wanda ya tallafawa jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, ya kasance ne don kai hari kan fitarwa daga jihohi kamar Iowa, in ji masana na China da Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma gwamnan Iowa na dogon lokaci, wanda shine babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da 'yan kasuwa.
Branstad ya bayyana a cikin wata kasida a cikin Sunday's Des Moines Register cewa, "China yanzu tana kara kai hari ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridarmu".
"Ta hanyar yada farfaganda, gwamnatin China tana amfani da al'adar Amurka mai karfi don 'yancin latsa da' yancin latsa ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace da aka biya a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin wannan, a nan cikin kantin labarai a kan titin Beijing, akwai 'yan muryoyin masu adawa da juna kuma babu wani tunani na gaskiya game da ra'ayoyin da jama'ar kasar Sin ke da shi game da yanayin tattalin arzikin kasar Sin, wanda kafofin watsa labarai ke karkashin cikakken iko na Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ta haka ne, ta kara da cewa "ɗaya daga cikin shahararrun jaridun kasar Sin ta kauce wa tayin buga labarinta", amma ba ta bayyana wane jarida ba.
