Ya kuma ce zama uwa ya sa ya kasa mai da hankali kan lashe gasar Olympics.
Mai gabatar da shirinmu Kirsty Young ta dauki hutun watanni saboda rashin lafiya.
Bayan ya nuna rashin jin daɗi a shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce yana jin 'ƙanƙanta' idan aka kwatanta da sauran mutane saboda al'umma ba ta yarda da son yara maza da mata ba.
Ya ce, "Har ya zuwa yau, wannan jin da ke sa ka ji an raina ka kuma ka bambanta da sauran mutane shi ne ainihin dalilin da ya ba ni ƙarfi da kuma ƙarfin da na samu na yi nasara".
Yana son ya tabbatar da cewa akwai wani abu, kamar yadda ya ce, domin ba ya son mutane su yi rashin amincewa da shi idan suka san game da jima'i.
Dan wasan da ya lashe lambobin tagulla biyu a wasannin Olympics ya zama babban mai tallata LGTB, kuma ya yi amfani da halartar wasannin Commonwealth da aka yi a Ostiraliya don neman ƙarin ƙasashe su yanke hukunci game da luwadi.
Ta ce ta yi wannan magana ne saboda tana jin ta yi sa'a ta rayu a fili ba tare da samun sakamako ba, kuma tana son ta ba wa wasu "bege".
Tsohon zakaran duniya sau uku ya ce ƙaunar da ya yi da wani mutum - mai shirya fim din Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013 - "ya kama shi da mamaki".
Daley ya auri wanda ya lashe kyautar Oscar a bara, wanda ya girme shi da shekaru 20, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai kasance matsala ba a tsakaninsu.
Ta ce, "Idan kana da ƙuruciya kuma ka sha irin wannan wahala" - ta halarci gasar Olympics a karon farko tana da shekara 14 kuma mahaifinta ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka - yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan shekarunta da ya sha irin wannan wahala.
Ma'auratan sun haifi ɗa a watan Yuni mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, wanda Daley ya ce ya canza "duk ra'ayinsa".
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, duk abin da nake tunani shi ne, 'Ina son lashe lambar zinare,' " in ji ta.
"Kuma, ka sani, akwai abubuwa da suka fi muhimmanci fiye da lambar zinare ta Olympics.
"Robin ne lambar zinare ta na gasar Olympics".
Sunan ɗansa ya yi kama da sunan mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekaru 40 bayan an gano shi da ciwon daji na kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda da cewa zai mutu ba, kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya tambaya shi ne idan suna da tikiti zuwa wasannin London na 2012 domin yana son zama a gaba.
Ya ce, "Ban iya gaya masa ba, ba za ka iya zama a gaban layi ba, Baba".
"Na riƙe hannunsa lokacin da ya daina numfashi, kuma na daina numfashi har sai da ya mutu, na yarda cewa ba shi da nasara", in ji ta.
Kashegari Daley ya shiga gasar Olympics ta 2012, inda ya lashe lambar tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shine abin da na yi mafarki a rayuwata, tsayawa a gaban jama'a a wasannin Olympics, babu wani abin da ya fi wannan jin dadi", in ji ta.
Har ila yau, ya ba da shawarar zaɓin waƙarsa ta farko - Proud, na Heather Small -, wanda ya sa ta ji an gano ta a duk lokacin da take shirin shirya wasannin Olympics kuma har yanzu yana sanya ta ta fara jin tsoro.
