Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai kafa tarihin wasan ne a ranar Lahadi a wasan Ryder Cup na 47 amma dole ne ya inganta yadda yake don kada ya zama mummunan.
Mickelson yana karya rikodin shekaru biyu yana wasa a karo na 12 a cikin wani abu guda; duk da haka, an tura shi zuwa ga kujera ta hanyar kyaftin din Jim Fury a ranar Asabar a cikin wasanni hudu da hudu.
Maimakon ya kasance a tsakiyar wasan kamar yadda ya saba yi a Amurka, wanda ya lashe gasar cin kofin duniya sau biyar ya raba ranarsa tsakanin zama mai farin ciki da kuma aiki a filin wasa, yana fatan gyara abin da ke sa shi wahala.
Bai taba zama mafi kyau a cikin direbobi ba, har ma a lokacin da ya fi dacewa a cikin aikinsa, kuma dan wasan mai shekaru 48 ba shi da kyau a cikin gasar cin kofin Le Golf National, inda 'yan wasan da suka fi karfi suka rinjayi wadanda suka rasa.
Kuma idan filin wasa ba shi da ban tsoro, Mickelson a wasan tara, ranar Lahadi, zai yi yaƙi da Francesco Molina wanda ya lashe gasar British Open, wanda ya haɗu da Tommy Fleetwood don lashe wasanni huɗu na wannan makon.
Idan 'yan Amurkan suka fara wasanni 12 da suka kasa maki hudu, kuma suka fara wasa da kyau, Mickelson zai iya zama mai yanke hukunci.
Fury ya nuna amincewarsa ga mutumin, domin ba zai iya faɗi fiye da haka ba.
"Ya fahimci matsayin da ya taka a yau sosai, ya yi mini ta'aziya a baya, ya ce zan shirya gobe", in ji Fury.
"Yana da tabbaci sosai.
