Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a ranar Juma'a sakamakon girgizar kasa da kuma guguwar tsunami da ta afkawa garin Palu na kasar Indonesia, inda jami'ai ke cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu zai iya ƙaruwa.
Saboda an katse hanyoyin sadarwa, jami'an ceto ba su iya samun bayanai daga gwamnatin Donggala ba, wanda shine yankin da ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5, arewacin Palu.
An kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 daga yankin bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da garin Palu da kuma gwamnatin Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, kuma yana kan ƙarshen bakin tekun bakin teku a gabar yamma ta tsibirin Sulawesi; a shekarar 2017, yana da mazaunan kusan 379,800.
Lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka faru, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala, a gefe guda, gwamnati ce da ke mamaye yanki sama da kilomita 300 (180 mil) wanda ya ƙunshi gabar arewa maso yamma na tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gwamnati, wanda shine yankin gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardin, yana da yawan jama'a 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi na tsakiya ya dogara ne akan kamun kifi da noma, musamman a yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Har ila yau, ma'adinan nickel yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia, Paluk da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami da dama a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami da ya afkawa Donggala ya kashe mutane fiye da 200, kuma gidaje daruruwan sun lalace.
A shekarar 1996 kuma, wata tsunami ta afku a yammacin Donggala, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin girgizar kasa da ake kira "Pacific Fire Belt" wanda hakan yasa ake yawan samun girgizar kasa.
Ga manyan girgizar kasa da tsunami na shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia, arewacin Sumatra, kuma ta haifar da tsunami. Tsunami ya girgiza kasashe 14, kuma ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a duk faɗin gabar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin a Aceh.
2005: Daga karshen watan Maris zuwa farkon watan Afrilu, an yi girgizar kasa mai karfi a gabar yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane suka mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afku a kudancin Java (tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia), kuma ta haifar da tsunami. Tsunami ya girgiza kudu maso gabar tekun, inda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar kusan 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afku a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin kudancin Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 ta afku a daya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai kusa da Sumatra, inda ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10. Ya haifar da lalata kauyuka da dama, inda mutane kusan 300 suka mutu.
2016: Wani karamin girgizar kasa a yankin Pidie Jaya na Aceh ya kawo bala'i da tsoro, inda mutane suka tuna da halakar da girgizar kasa da tsunami mai kisa ta 2004 ta haifar.
Ba a samu wata guguwa ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 suka mutu a lokacin da gine-gine suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, wanda ya shahara sosai tsakanin masu yawon bude ido, inda ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane sama da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata daruruwan gine-gine, kuma ya sa yawancin masu yawon bude ido ba su iya gudu ba na wani lokaci.
