An yi zargin cewa Saipov mai shekara 30 ya yi amfani da motar haya daga Home Depot don kai harin a kan hanyar West Side Highway a Manhattan ta Kudu, inda a wannan harin na watan Oktoba, ya kori masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke.
